A. Aktifkan pgcrypto lalu gunakan gen_salt (1x saja per DB):
CREATE EXTENSION IF NOT EXISTS pgcrypto;


Setelah itu query berikut akan jalan:
INSERT INTO users (id, username, email, password_hash, role, department, created_at)
VALUES (
    gen_random_uuid(),
    'tester',
    'tester@gagakhitam.com',
    crypt('rahasia123', gen_salt('bf', 10)),
    'admin',
    'Management',
    NOW()
);

INSERT INTO users (username, password, role)
VALUES (
  'super',
  crypt('123456', gen_salt('bf')),
  'admin'
);

B. Kalau tidak mau pakai pgcrypto, hash dulu di Node:
Di terminal:
node -e "const bcrypt = require('bcrypt'); console.log(bcrypt.hashSync('rahasia123', 10));"

Contoh output:
$2b$10$eK8Pem5Q7K6tV9i3qZ5xUuI6H2oPzQ3Y4R5s6T7u8V9w0X1y2Z3A4B

Masukkan hash tersebut langsung:
INSERT INTO users (id, username, email, password_hash, role, department, created_at)
VALUES (
    gen_random_uuid(),
    'tester',
    'tester@gagakhitam.com',
    '$2b$10$eK8Pem5Q7K6tV9i3qZ5xUuI6H2oPzQ3Y4R5s6T7u8V9w0X1y2Z3A4B',
    'admin',
    'Management',
    NOW()
);
